ygData.msgSnippet: It doesn t really bother me other than the fact that it was given to me by my new guild. I feel bad as I ve only had it 3 days and lost it already!! Oh well,
ygData.messageBody:
It doesn't really bother me other than the fact that it was given to me by
my new guild. I feel bad as I've only had it 3 days and lost it already!!

Oh well, maybe I'll get another one soon.
